06:02.533 --> 06:07.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They also bet on how they're
going to change the way people
-- how they sell the cars.

06:07.000 --> 06:12.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I mean, you look all across
the board when it comes to
Tesla, there's this huge bet.

06:13.366 --> 06:15.300 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Right now, they make
4,400 cars a month or so.

06:15.300 --> 06:19.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
