sell 500,000 Model 3's.

06:19.266 --> 06:21.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM:
It's a huge scale-up.

06:21.333 --> 06:25.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
