1,900, you know, later on.

06:32.000 --> 06:35.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The key is, how long are those
customers going to wait for that
car, and how long is it going

06:35.600 --> 06:40.000 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to take to get there, and they
are going to be able to scale
up, and can they keep that

06:40.000 --> 06:44.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
quality that they were known for
when they were selling 4,400?

06:44.033 --> 06:48.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I don't know what the answer
to those things are, but I do
know that is going to be really

06:48.033 --> 06:49.466 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
hard.

06:49.466 --> 06:50.700 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
